                    <h1 style="text-align: justify; " mce_style="text-align: justify; ">Welcome to Halls For Hire!</h1>
                    <p style="text-align: justify; " mce_style="text-align: justify; ">Halls for Hire is a comprehensive directory of community halls and venues across Australia. We give communities a place to list their hall, and users a place to find an affordable and local hall in just a few clicks.</p>
                    <p style="text-align: justify; " mce_style="text-align: justify; ">If you are looking for a hall to host your next Birthday Party, Meeting, Product Launch, Performance Space, Dinners, Weddings, Engagements, Adult Class, Exhibitions or even a Rehearsal Space we can help! Simply put a few details into our search fields such as area, type of function and number of people you're expecting and we will pull together a list of appropriate venues and give you all their contact details to get the ball rolling!</p>
                    <p style="text-align: justify; " mce_style="text-align: justify; ">Below are some frequently asked questions &nbsp;- hope they help!</p>
                    <p style="text-align: justify; " mce_style="text-align: justify; "><span mce_name="strong" mce_style="font-weight: bold;" style="font-weight: bold;" class="Apple-style-span">HOW DO I FIND A HALL?</span> Finding a hall is easy. Simply <u style=""><a href="http://www.hallsforhire.com.au" mce_href="http://www.hallsforhire.com.au">click here</a></u> and complete the search fields.</p>
                    <p style="text-align: justify; " mce_style="text-align: justify; "><span mce_name="strong" mce_style="font-weight: bold;" style="font-weight: bold;" class="Apple-style-span">HOW DO I LIST MY HALL? </span>Listing your hall on this website is easy with a little know how - simply <a href="/component/user/login" mce_href="/component/user/login"><u style="">click here</u></a> to complete the on-line form and then upload some photographs. Once you have created your profile you can go back in and edit the information at any time.</p><p style="text-align: justify; " mce_style="text-align: justify; "><span mce_name="strong" mce_style="font-weight: bold;" style="font-weight: bold;" class="Apple-style-span">HOW MUCH WILL IT COST TO LIST MY HALL?</span> Halls for Hire was designed with communities in mind and is priced accordingly. For all pricing information&nbsp;<a href="/pricing" mce_href="/pricing"><u style="">click here</u></a>.</p>
                    <p style="text-align: justify; " mce_style="text-align: justify; "><span mce_name="strong" mce_style="font-weight: bold;" style="font-weight: bold;" class="Apple-style-span">WHAT IF I CAN'T LIST MY HALL - OR DON'T HAVE COMPUTER KNOWLEDGE?</span> Firstly, try out our online tutorial by <span mce_name="strong" mce_style="font-weight: bold;" style="font-weight: bold;" class="Apple-style-span"><u style=""><a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=na1Csw9E0bU" mce_href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=na1Csw9E0bU" target="_blank">clicking here</a></u></span> and <u style=""><a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tNuWKNugV9Y" mce_href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tNuWKNugV9Y" target="_blank">then here</a></u>, (or scroll down for videos) these tutorial will guide you through the website and show you everything you need to know. If you are still unable to list your hall online, please give us a call and we can arrange for a staff member to come to you - take some photographs and create the listing on your behalf. We can even teach you the system so that you can edit the profile in the future.<span mce_name="strong" mce_style="font-weight: bold;" style="font-weight: bold;" class="Apple-style-span"><i> This may attract a small charge depending on hours needed.</i></span></p>
                    <p style="text-align: justify; " mce_style="text-align: justify; "><span mce_name="strong" mce_style="font-weight: bold;" style="font-weight: bold;" class="Apple-style-span"><i> </i></span><span mce_name="strong" mce_style="font-weight: bold;" style="font-weight: bold;" class="Apple-style-span">CAN I ADVERTISE ON THIS WEBSITE?</span> We do allow associated businesses to advertise on this website. <u style=""><a href="/advertise" mce_href="/advertise">Click here for further information</a></u> or give us a call to discuss your needs.</p>
                    <p style="text-align: justify; " mce_style="text-align: justify; "><span mce_name="strong" mce_style="font-weight: bold;" style="font-weight: bold;" class="Apple-style-span">I LOST MY PASSWORD – WHAT DO I DO?</span> A password is needed to access your hall’s profile. Your user name is usually your email address, and your password can be retrieved by <u style=""><a href="/component/user/reset#content" mce_href="/component/user/reset#content">clicking here</a>.</u></p><p style="text-align: justify; " mce_style="text-align: justify; "><span mce_name="strong" mce_style="font-weight: bold;" style="font-weight: bold;" class="Apple-style-span" mce_fixed="1">ONLINE TUTORIAL</span> go to youtube for an online tutorial to learn how to register with <span mce_name="strong" mce_style="font-weight: bold;" style="font-weight: bold;" class="Apple-style-span" mce_fixed="1"><u style=""><a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=na1Csw9E0bU" mce_href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=na1Csw9E0bU" target="_blank">Tutorial 1</a></u></span> and how to create a listing with <span mce_name="strong" mce_style="font-weight: bold;" style="font-weight: bold;" class="Apple-style-span" mce_fixed="1"><u style=""><a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tNuWKNugV9Y&amp;feature=related" mce_href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tNuWKNugV9Y&amp;feature=related" target="_blank">Tutorial 2</a></u></span></p><p>
